<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="3706224" n="0" type="archival"/> <pb facs="3706225" n="0" type="archival"/> 
  <pb facs="3706226" n="1"/>
  <lb/><opener>Magnifico Viro,
  <lb/>Domino <rs type="person">Johanni Bernoullio</rs>
  <lb/>officiosissimam salutem <abbr>d.</abbr> 
  <lb/><rs type="person">Joh. Wendel. Bülffinger</rs> <abbr>Med.</abbr> <rs type="place">Canstad.</rs></opener>
  <p><lb/>Fretus benevolentia Tua, Vir magnifice, qua <rs type="person">frater</rs> s<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>pius
    <lb/>magna sua voluptate usus est, <rs type="letter">litteris</rs> ejusdem<note type="comment">Georg Bernhard Bilfinger an Johann Bernoulli von 1725 08 21, UB Basel, L I a 653, Nr.28*</note>  <rs type="place">Petropoli</rs>
    <lb/>missis, <rs type="letter">meas</rs> adjungere audeo; quas ut benevole accipias,
    <lb/>est quod obnixe rogo. Tardius <rs type="letter">fratern<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>, cui h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>clus<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> erant, <rs type="letter">litter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> quam par erat advenere, quare <rs type="letter">ipsas
      <lb/>posteriores</rs> quas scripsit, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>currerunt. <rs type="letter">Quibus nov<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <rs type="place">Tubin<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gam</rs> vocationes miss<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sunt: <rs type="letter">altera</rs> <abbr>Dno</abbr> <rs type="person">Duvernoy</rs>, Professori
    <lb/>Medicin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> extraordinario, qui Anatomicus <rs type="organisation">Academi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Petropoli<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tan<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> vocatus est: <rs type="letter">altera</rs> <rs type="person">duobus ex Magistris nostris philosophi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>,
    <pb facs="3706227" n="2"/>
    <lb/>qui in Adjunctorum numerum recepti sunt. Equidem
    <lb/>nescio an omnes vocationem accepturi sint, et an proxime
    <lb/>quod <rs type="person">Petropolitanorum</rs> mens <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> votum est, itineri se accin<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cturi sint? interim ista occasione pro transmittendis,
    <lb/>quas frater petiit, reculis utar, ut non opus sit istis
    <lb/>honoratissimos <rs type="person">Filios</rs> Tuos onerare. </p> <p rend="space">Cetera, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
      <lb/><rs type="person">frater</rs> addidit de ceremoniis, quibus ad ingressum
      <lb/>ad <rs type="person">Augustissimam Russorum Dominam</rs> adducti, iterum<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
      <lb/>reducti sunt, una cum brevibus, quas coram <rs type="person"><abbr>Augustiss.</abbr>
      <lb/>Imperatrice</rs> habuere orationibus, ea omnia jam per
      <lb/><rs type="biblio">Novellas Lipsiensium</rs>, quas de Rebus Litterariis inscribunt, 
    <pb facs="3706228" n="3"/>
    <lb/>publico innotuerunt, ut notitiam Tuam fugere haud
      <lb/>queant. Quare ne longiori scriptione Tibi, Vir magnifi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ce, molestiam creem, qui non nisi gravissimis vacas ne<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gotiis, filum abrumpo si prius me favori Tuo submisse
      <lb/>co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endaverim, animum<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> ad qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>vis officia, eti<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> transmit<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tendas, si <rs type="letter">responsorias</rs> ad <rs type="person">fratr<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice></rs> dare lubuerit, <rs type="letter">litteras</rs> paratis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>simum testificatus fuero.</p> <closer><salute>Vale.</salute> 
  
  <lb/><dateline><abbr>Dab.</abbr> <rs type="place">Canstad.</rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1725-09-28">28. <abbr>Septemb.</abbr>
    <lb/>1725</date>.</dateline> </closer>
  <pb facs="3706229" n="4" type="empty"/>
</div>
